\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\varphi(\vec{x})\equiv\llor_{i<\omega}\varphi_{i}(\vec{x}),
\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $\{\varphi_{i}\}_{i<\omega}$
\end_inset

 is a computable sequence of positive finitary conjunctive formulas.
