\begin_layout Standard
Let us briefly elaborate on that last bullet point.
 If 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi(\vec{x})\equiv\llor_{i}\left(\psi_{i}(\vec{x})\land\neg\varphi_{i}(\vec{x})\right)$
\end_inset

