.
 Suppose worker 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

 is the one who has created these matches.
 Suppose that the elements 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{x}$
\end_inset

 are matched to the tuple 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{b}$
\end_inset

,
